### test1:
GET http://localhost:5007/api/doctors/query/?email=danial@example.com
### test2:
GET http://localhost:5007/api/doctors/query/?refreshToken=ksjdlkfj
### test3: 
GET http://localhost:5007/api/doctors/query/?email=johndo@example.co

### get one doctor by id 
GET http://localhost:5007/api/doctors/645cc29d986dd883ffa87b7e

### create one doctor
POST http://localhost:5007/api/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Danial",
  "last_name": "Dalas",
  "email_address": "danial@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "gender": "male",
  "phone_number": "123456789",
  "birth_date": "1990-01-01",
  "speciality":"Pediatrics",
  "location": {
    "address": "123 Main St",
    "country": "USA",
    "city": "New York"
  }
}

